WEBVTT

00:00:14.504 --> 00:00:15.747
Zamislite svet

00:00:15.747 --> 00:00:17.892
u kom vidite brojeve i slova u boji

00:00:17.892 --> 00:00:19.750
iako su štampani crnom bojom,

00:00:19.750 --> 00:00:21.833
u kom muzika ili glasovi pokreću vrtlog


00:00:21.833 --> 00:00:23.922
pokretnih oblika u boji,

00:00:23.922 --> 00:00:25.858
u kom reči i imena ispunjavaju vaša usta

00:00:25.858 --> 00:00:27.592
neobičnim ukusima.

00:00:27.592 --> 00:00:30.437
Zatvor ima ukus 
kao hladna, tvrda slanina,